Best of the Sunshine State!
Updated: 06/11/2024
Event Venues in Florida
You want everything to be perfect for that special day. Whether you are holding a conference, a family reunion, a birthday party or a corporate event, your entire day is based upon your event venue. Location, Size, Amenities & More!  It’s imperative to choose a location that will best represent your occasion. Not only do we have a great list of venues for you to browse nearby, we have the entire sunshine state for your choosing. Life is about Adventure! Open your horizons and check out these awesome places in Florida to hold your next big event.
But not all event venues are the same. We can help you discover the best places to throw a party in the sunshine state. Being a Florida native and promoting local companies since 2005, we’ve learned a lot about the communities and the businesses offering services within each area. Whether you were born and raised in the area or just passing through, the event venues found in the Florida Special Occasions
Guide
, can and will provide you with a positive experience. Expect a top-notch staff – trained and prepared to give you an outstanding service. Feel free to browse the business listings below. You can also search for a specific company by using our county or city features.

We’re not just “All about Event Venues“, we promote the best companies throughout the entire state of Florida and have been doing so since 2005. Call it a business directory, call it a phonebook online, call it what you will…but what we are – is – your information resource highway to Florida. Filled with tons of awesome reads; Taste of History, Pyper the Pelican, Florida in the Slow Lane, County by County, Florida Bucket List, Mandi the Manatee and more!  After all, it is… All About the Sunshine State!
We invite you to explore Florida and discover the beauty within.
